                <div class="orion-card">
                    <div class="orion-card-title">⚠️ MINIMUM BET (2 FIAT)</div>
                    <div class="orion-input-group row-full">
                        <label id="minbet-info" class="warning-text">Min bet: calculating...</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-muted" style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 10px;">
                        💡 2 Rupiah = $0.00014 (konversi USD otomatis)
